title: Jacob Goes Missing | American Horror Stories - Episode 6: "Feral" (HQ Clip)
author: AHS Crave
description: "Feral" is the sixth episode of Ryan Murphy & Brad Falchuk's "American Horror Stories," the official "AHS"/"American Horror Story" spin-off series, exclusive to FX on Hulu. Written & directed by Manny Coto, the episode stars Cody Fern as Stan Vogel, Aaron Tveit as Jay Gantz, Tiffany DuPont as Addy Gantz, Blake Shields (Bob Birch), and Colin Tandberg as Jacob Gantz. All rights belong to 20th Television, FX Productions, and Ryan Murphy Productions.
